ls-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"bg-background text-foreground min-h-screen flex flex-col font-sans\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#f7f8fb] text-slate-950\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-[1480px] px-6 py-6 sm:px-10 xl:px-12\"><header class=\"flex justify-end rounded-[24px] border border-white/60 bg-white/70 px-5 py-3 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><a class=\"rounded-full px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 transition hover:text-slate-900\" href=\"/?auth=login\">Log in</a><a class=\"rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\" href=\"/?auth=signup\">Getting Started</a></div></header><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-2 py-10 sm:px-4 lg:py-14\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Aura</p><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-4xl font-black tracking-[-0.04em] text-[#2e3277] sm:text-5xl\">Produto social com mais contexto</h1><p class=\"mt-4 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600\">Uma visao publica da experiencia da Aura para quem quer entender o produto antes de entrar na rede.</p></div><div class=\"mt-10\"><section id=\"preview\" class=\"border-y border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-8 px-5 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:px-8 lg:py-18\"><div class=\"max-w-xl\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary\">Preview do produto</p><h2 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-slate-950 sm:text-4xl\">Uma primeira impressão que já comunica produto sólido.</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600\">Sem depender de vídeo pesado ou animação exagerada. A landing mostra feed, descoberta e comunidades com uma linguagem visual de produto real.</p><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600\">Conteúdo útil</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm\">Alta prioridade</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600\">Comunidades em comum</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm\">+ relevância social</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 px-4 py-3\"><span class=\"text-sm font-medium text-slate-600\">Ruído viral</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-900 shadow-sm\">Menor alcance</span></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]\"><div class=\"rounded-[28px] border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"h-11 w-11 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-sky-400\"></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900\">Ana Ribeiro</p><p class=\"text-xs text-slate-500\">Compartilhou uma análise em Product Builders</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-2\"><div class=\"h-3 rounded-full bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-3 w-11/12 rounded-full bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-3 w-8/12 rounded-full bg-slate-200\"></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 rounded-[20px] bg-sky-50 p-4\"><div class=\"grid gap-2 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white px-3 py-2 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">Relevante</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white px-3 py-2 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">Qualidade alta</div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-white px-3 py-2 text-center text-xs font-semibold text-slate-600\">Comunidade em comum</div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[24px] p-5 border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-950\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] opacity-60\">Bloco <!-- -->1</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg font-bold leading-7\">Posts com contexto e reputação</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] p-5 bg-slate-950 text-white\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] opacity-60\">Bloco <!-- -->2</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg font-bold leading-7\">Comunidades com discussões organizadas</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[24px] p-5 border border-slate-200 bg-white text-slate-950\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] opacity-60\">Bloco <!-- -->3</p><p class=\"mt-3 text-lg font-bold leading-7\">Sugestões mais inteligentes de pessoas e temas</p></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3\"><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 transition hover:bg-slate-50\" href=\"/communities/explore\">Ver comunidades</a><a class=\"inline-flex h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#6f63dd] px-6 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[#5e53cd]\" href=\"/?auth=signup\">Comecar agora</a></div></div></section></div></main><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-79efdc3d928800db.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[87424,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68a.js\\\",\\\"7177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-1c381122de0d0c90.js\\\"],\\\"ErrorBoundary\\\"]\\n3:I[32666,[\\\"7984\\\",\\\"static/chunks/ef7830f0-774d581c3e223a57.js\\\",\\\"8960\\\",\\\"static/chunks/406b2ba4-1573ea644beca731.js\\\",\\\"7695\\\",\\\"static/chunks/7695-f386262b14f29a58.js\\\",\\\"5288\\\",\\\"static/chunks/5288-63462ff6f135c68